Job Description :

To handle ocean shipment to US, EU and Intra Asia markets;
To coordinate with suppliers, carriers, factories on day to day operation, which includes:-
Handle and follow up booking with vendors;
Prepare forecast to carriers;
Submit booking to related carriers;
Prepare SI, dispatch ASN data;
Execute SOP & Logistics related tasks;
Work with origin teams closely
Job Requirement :

Degree or above in any discipline;
With 1 years' experience in international logistics (air / ocean freight) operations;
Able to act as a team player to execute the operation;
Proficiency in written and verbal English , Cantonese and Mandarin;
Fresh Graduate is also welcome
Interested parties please send full resume with employment history and expected salary to HRA Division, Yusen Logistics (Hong Kong) Limited at Level 31, Tower 1, Kowloon Commerce Centre, 51 Kwai Cheong Road, Kwai Chung, N.T. or by email to hr.ylhk @ hk.yusen-logistics.com     


Yusen Logistics (Hong Kong) is an equal opportunity employer. All information collected will be used for recruitment purpose only.
